          data-toggle="tooltip" data-placement="bottom" title="Users that click on these links/buttons will be able to add deals to their Pouch. These can be sent out in emails/texts, posted to social media, or displayed anywhere online." style="font-size:.66em">  
          <i class="fa fa-info-circle" aria-hidden="true"></i>

          </span>
        </h2>
        <hr>
        
        <h5>
          Bitly URL:
